# GitHound Code Owners
# This file defines who should be automatically requested for review
# when changes are made to specific parts of the codebase.
#
# Order is important; the last matching pattern takes precedence.
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
* @AstroAir

# Core application code
/githound/ @AstroAir

# Search engine components (critical functionality)
/githound/search_engine/ @AstroAir

# MCP server functionality
